Adrienne Burke, the marketing manager presented her case in such a compelling manner, that we felt we had to be part of this initiative. Each year, we like to align ourselves with a different and worthwhile cause. As this cause had national relevance and our digital footprint is new and was only recently completed, her timing was perfect. We are delighted to welcome Habitat for Humanity South Africa as our CSI project - united in the vision of a South Africa in which everyone has a decent place to live. click to enlarge